,"body":"Anon-chan, don't stare at her so much... I mean, why are you fighting?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":39,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"I don't know. I was talking with my friend and she suddenly attacked me, saying \"What do you want?\" or \"Are you really her friend?\"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-06-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"She suddenly got mad at me and asked me if I had invited Tomori to join the band....  I really don't get it~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-06-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":39}],"windowDisplayName":"Soyo","body":"Tomori...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":39,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":39}],"windowDisplayName":"Soyo","body":"Maybe, do you mean... Tomori Takamatsu?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":39,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"What? Oh, yes... we are in the same class... Do you know her?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-06-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":39}],"windowDisplayName":"Soyo","body":"... She's a friend of mine.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":39,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":39}],"windowDisplayName":"Soyo","body":"... I see. She's in Haneoka...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":39}],"windowDisplayName":"Soyo","body":"You said you invited... Tomori-chan, didn't you? Are you going to be in a band together?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":39,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Well... I invited her, but she turned me down...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-06-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"By the way, Soyo-san. Which part did you play in the band?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-06-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":39}],"windowDisplayName":"Soyo","body":"I was in charge of the bass guitar.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":39,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":39,"voiceId":"event235-06-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"req